to the editor re south 's football fans still stand up and pray front page aug 27 the movement toward unofficial prayer at high school football games in response to the supreme court 's decision against school sanctioned student led prayer is the most compelling evidence so far that the court 's decision was correct proponents of this aggressive effort to skirt the law are engaging in an egregious exercise of tyranny of the majority one would expect such a movement in places like kosovo or bosnia rather than in the united states which was founded on religious freedom for all samuel p del propost maplewood nj aug 27 2000

